{"tid":744651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會無la la 鳩笑？","createTime":"2018-07-16T06:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T12:51:56.000Z","uid":135761,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c03d6069b1e5841d68973b4eddc670b8b75aa5de","tid":744651,"uid":135761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"有時個腦海會諗起啲好笑野就會忍唔住喺度鳩笑，跟住身邊啲人就會係度諗你做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我啱啱喺七仔增值嗰時諗起啲鳩野笑到震咁對住個職員講:增值200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我感覺到後面啲人想送我去青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇同路人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccc0cc50e53e9b96d61d0e9710b3dc8676085a7","tid":744651,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:02:11.000Z","msg":"有咩咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講嚟聽下"},{"pid":"9a1cfac600b25c35fd1dcf44c43cc627aeea1158","tid":744651,"uid":25543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"見到呢個po即刻鳩笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bb7f5f345a499a17300e23bc7ed1c395116a29","tid":744651,"uid":173480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"有時on99想笑又忍住，但最尾忍唔住嗰吓鳩笑得仲勁過未忍之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b745a22fea4ab8d081d852297e8e00cf14764e4","tid":744651,"uid":135761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5ccc0cc50e53e9b96d61d0e9710b3dc8676085a7","tid":744651,"u